          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1599060475869-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1599060475869-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1599060475869-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Chop the <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly<strong> </strong>(if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the<strong> chopped creamed coconut</strong> in 250ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1599060490492-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1599060490492-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1599060490492-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1599060490492-x1000.jpg",
