          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1599060490492-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>coconut stock</strong> to the pan and cook for 2-3 min or until a thick sauce remains</p><p>Once the rice has been cooking for 10 min, add the <strong>chopped green beans</strong> to the pot</p><p>Cover with the lid and cook for a further 5 min or until tender with a slight bite – this is your <strong>cardamom & green bean rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
